# Flowbite Component Standards

**STRICT RULE: Use only Flowbite components from `flowbite-astro` and Tailwind utility classes. NO custom CSS classes, NO inline styles, NO style attributes.**

## Required Components
- Buttons → `<Button>` component
- Cards → `<Card>`, `<CardHeader>`, `<CardBody>`, `<CardFooter>`
- Forms → `<TextInput>`, `<Textarea>`, `<Label>`, `<Select>`
- Badges → `<Badge>` component
- Alerts → `<Alert>` component
- Navigation → `<Navbar>`, `<ListGroup>`, `<ListGroupItem>`
- Collapsible → `<Accordion>` or `<Collapse>` (never `<details>`)
- Layout → Tailwind utilities only (`container`, `mx-auto`, `flex`, `grid`)

## Forbidden
- Custom CSS classes in global.css (except Tailwind `@import`)
- Inline `style` attributes
- Native HTML elements styled as components (use Flowbite components instead)
- Custom utility classes

## Allowed
- Tailwind utility classes for layout/spacing
- Flowbite component props for styling
- Flowbite theme configuration in `tailwind.config.js`
